    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 7</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 22 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 10 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 24</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique is a wild card, a true random chance technique that can result in a very deadly combo or a very useless one. Roll d20 per level. Each time you roll a 7, you gain a cumulative +1 luck bonus to attack rolls made for this technique. Each time you roll a 13, you gain a cumu-lative -1 penalty to attack rolls made for this tech-nique. Each time you roll a 20, you can make an attack at your highest attack bonus against the target.<br><br>If you roll two consecutive 1s, you cannot roll any more dice. Any other number rolled has no effect. Results for attack rolls will not grant the random effects this technique may grant.</p>\n\n\n\n",
